# URL the "Open Studio" CTA points to.
#
# Leave unset for normal use:
#   - production build  -> "/studio" (served by the Vercel rewrite in vercel.json)
#   - dev / preview     -> the live Studio URL, so the link works locally
#
# Set this to override (e.g. point at a local Studio dev server):
# VITE_STUDIO_URL=http://localhost:5173/
